                    <h3>Biography:</h3>
                    <p>
                        Meriadoc Brandybuck and Peregrin Took, more commonly known as Merry
                                                                                                                                                                                    and Pippin, were a pair of Hobbits, from The Shire, and more
                                                                                                                                                                                    specifically, Frodo's counsins and best friends. Both were members
                                                                                                                                                                                    of the Fellowship of the Ring. Merry loved boats and ponies, and had
                                                                                                                                                                                    a great interest in the maps of Middle-earth.
                    </p>
