                    <p>
                        "It comes in pints?!" Pippin to Merry, when the latter brings a pint
                                                                                                                                                                                    of ale to their table at the Prancing Pony.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        "We've had one, yes. What about second breakfast?!" Pippin to Aragorn
                    </p>
                    <p>
